fusing</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aksteve\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5f6098c49f3b3f9ca2c252b76eebe452?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5f6098c49f3b3f9ca2c252b76eebe452?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aksteve\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Steve <small>(aksteve)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 18, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The first thing you are going to want to know is \"where is the calendar\"?\n\nDoes it get automatically created? Do you have to create a page and insert shortcode? Do you have any control over what page the calendar goes on?\n\nBasic set up info.\n\nI have spent 30 minutes and can\'t find the answer. Not impressed.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Junk !</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tradinghub\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1a0c6df9f0fe6310aa8f1644420f818e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1a0c6df9f0fe6310aa8f1644420f818e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tradinghub\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tradinghub</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 18, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Cannot even do the basics ! Forget it, move on...</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Too many addons</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ahancock\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/524bde006378a8f3b3c3ada9eaeedb32?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/524bde006378a8f3b3c3ada9eaeedb32?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ahancock\" class=\"reviewer-name\">YesThatAllen <small>(ahancock)</small></a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 15, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I don\'t have an issue with the quality of the product so much as the shear number of products to purchase to get a working system.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great app - Great Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jb1337\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2b04473b3bc4cdfa52cdf4d2bfe2a8e0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/2b04473b3bc4cdfa52cdf4d2bfe2a8e0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jb1337\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jb1337</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 14, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Very versitlie app with a lot of extras!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Seems excellent but...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kirschrg\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b7c13f1af06667572fd817a67cb0e466?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b7c13f1af06667572fd817a67cb0e466?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kirschrg\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kirschrg</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 7, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hello\n<strong>The Events Calendar Version 4.5.12.1</strong> free demo.\nIt looked perfect at first glance using the TOTAL theme default page settings but...\nAfter the initial setting changing some titles, and adding some events:\n\n1) I am <strong>UNABLE TO MODIFY the title</strong> like on any other page! A very annoying detail. I might have missed something or overlooked an important setting. Somebody may have done it ? Or the plug-in code should be improved on next release.\n\n2) After playing with settings, disable + suppress the plug-in and removing the tribe folder in the WP, I have <strong>empty pages</strong> when I click on an event in the calendar month view. The title is Nice but the text infos showing  up on mouse over the event have disappeared in the event page.\n\n3) <strong>Even more important</strong> : There seems to be no way to uninstall completely the plug-in in order to restart from scratch a new clean install. When I disable + suppress + install the plug-in, all the old settings and titles show up again. However it is a standard approach in a mixed-up situation, how can I force a complete new install from scratch ?\n\nThanks a lot for advice.\nRobert</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great product - thanks.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/officefocus\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b9a12e0b8bfcb89bd329813bbcfea4c7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b9a12e0b8bfcb89bd329813bbcfea4c7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/officefocus\" class=\"reviewer-name\">officeFocus</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">September 4, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been a loyal user through a few versions. It dies exactly what it promises.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Development Heavy</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ehlanafoley\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31332f3b8eaa6e8d0b6e05d0c9c4e59a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/31332f3b8eaa6e8d0b6e05d0c9c4e59a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ehlanafoley\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ehlanafoley</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">August 30, 2017</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve spent all morning trying to figure out how to simply drop the calendar onto a page with a shortcode or embed. I\'m not a developer so this calendar isn\'t for me at all, really unclear instructions, will be looking elsewhere!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Well Designed</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\"><div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div></div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/akanning\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a70c8048b721f08fa99fadcfdcefb15f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a70c8048b721f08fa99fadcfdcefb15f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\