;extended-views-2&#x2F;\">\n				<i class=\"ai1ec-fa ai1ec-fa-download ai1ec-fa-fw\"></i>\n				Get this Add-on\n			</a>\n		</div>\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon\">\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon-title\">Superwidget</div>\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon-image\">\n				<a href=\"https&#x3A;&#x2F;&#x2F;time.ly&#x2F;wordpress-calendar-plugin&#x2F;addons&#x2F;superwidget&#x2F;\" target=\"_blank\">\n					<img height=\"150\" src=\"http&#x3A;&#x2F;&#x2F;time.ly&#x2F;wp-timely&#x2F;wp-content&#x2F;uploads&#x2F;edd&#x2F;2014&#x2F;08&#x2F;superwidget-addon.gif\">\n				</a>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon-excerpt\">Embed your calendar on other websites or services, almost anywhere.</div>\n			<a class=\"ai1ec-addon-button\" target=\"_blank\"\n			   href=\"https&#x3A;&#x2F;&#x2F;time.ly&#x2F;wordpress-calendar-plugin&#x2F;addons&#x2F;superwidget&#x2F;\">\n				<i class=\"ai1ec-fa ai1ec-fa-download ai1ec-fa-fw\"></i>\n				Get this Add-on\n			</a>\n		</div>\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon\">\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon-title\">Venues</div>\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon-image\">\n				<a href=\"https&#x3A;&#x2F;&#x2F;time.ly&#x2F;wordpress-calendar-plugin&#x2F;addons&#x2F;venues&#x2F;\" target=\"_blank\">\n					<img height=\"150\" src=\"http&#x3A;&#x2F;&#x2F;time.ly&#x2F;wp-timely&#x2F;wp-content&#x2F;uploads&#x2F;edd&#x2F;2014&#x2F;08&#x2F;venue-addon2.gif\">\n				</a>\n			</div>\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon-excerpt\">Save time and create richer venue listings.</div>\n			<a class=\"ai1ec-addon-button\" target=\"_blank\"\n			   href=\"https&#x3A;&#x2F;&#x2F;time.ly&#x2F;wordpress-calendar-plugin&#x2F;addons&#x2F;venues&#x2F;\">\n				<i class=\"ai1ec-fa ai1ec-fa-download ai1ec-fa-fw\"></i>\n				Get this Add-on\n			</a>\n		</div>\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon\">\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon-title\">CSV Import</div>\n			<div class=\"ai1ec-addon-image\">\n				<a href=\"https&#x3A;&#x2F;&#x2F;time.ly&#x2F;wordpress-calendar-plugin&#x2F;addons&#x2F;csv-import&#x2F;\" target=\"_blank\">\n					<im