(374, 1, '2017-09-28 15:27:05', '2017-09-28 13:27:05', 'We have just sent out our invitations for the participants of the 3rd Edition of EHP! We can\'t wait to #MakeHealthGreatGain!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe EHP team would like to thank all the applicants for the interest demonstrated on this challenging initiative. We received many great candidatures this year and it was not easy to shortlist 40 amongst them.\r\nFor those who were not selected, we wish you good luck and hope you are willing to try once again next year\r\n\r\n', 'EHP 3rd Edition Speakers Announced', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ehp-3rd-edition-speakers-announced', '', '', '2017-09-29 10:13:15', '2017-09-29 08:13:15', '', 0, 'http://4883dc5101.url-de-test.ws/?p=374', 0, 'post', '', 0),
